---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div class="git-main-container">
    <section class="git-header">
      <svg class="git-icon" role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="color:#f34f29"><title>Git</title><path fill="currentColor" d="M23.546 10.93L13.067.452c-.604-.603-1.582-.603-2.188 0L8.708 2.627l2.76 2.76c.645-.215 1.379-.07 1.889.441.516.515.658 1.258.438 1.9l2.658 2.66c.645-.223 1.387-.078 1.9.435.721.72.721 1.884 0 2.604-.719.719-1.881.719-2.6 0-.539-.541-.674-1.337-.404-1.996L12.86 8.955v6.525c.176.086.342.203.488.348.713.721.713 1.883 0 2.6-.719.721-1.889.721-2.609 0-.719-.719-.719-1.879 0-2.598.182-.18.387-.316.605-.406V8.835c-.217-.091-.424-.222-.6-.401-.545-.545-.676-1.342-.396-2.009L7.636 3.7.45 10.881c-.6.605-.6 1.584 0 2.189l10.48 10.477c.604.604 1.582.604 2.186 0l10.43-10.43c.605-.603.605-1.582 0-2.187"/></svg>
      <h1>Git</h1>
      <p>(Sistema de control de versiones distribuido)</p>
    </section>
    <section class="git-content">
      <h2>¿Qué podés encontrar acá?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Fundamentos y comandos básicos de Git</li>
        <li>Flujos de trabajo y ramas</li>
        <li>Buenas prácticas y ejemplos</li>
        <li>Recursos y enlaces útiles</li>
      </ul>
      <blockquote class="git-quote">"Git es esencial para el trabajo colaborativo y el control de versiones."</blockquote>
      <a href="/blog" class="back-main-btn">Volver al inicio</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
.git-main-container {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 2.5rem 1rem 2.5rem 1rem;
  font-family: Inter, Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
}
.git-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 2.2rem;
}
.git-icon {
  width: 54px;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  display: block;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  color: #f34f29;
}
.git-header h1 {
  font-size: 2.1rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  letter-spacing: -1px;
  color: #f34f29;
}
.git-header p {
  font-size: 1.13rem;
  color: var(--color-text, #444);
  max-width: 500px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.git-content h2 {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  color: #f34f29;
}
.git-content ul {
  margin: 0 0 1.2rem 1.2rem;
  padding: 0;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
}
.git-content li {
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}
.git-quote {
  margin: 1.5rem 0 0 0;
  padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
  background: #fff2e1;
  border-left: 4px solid #f34f29;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-style: italic;
  color: #b94c1e;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
}
.back-main-btn {
  display: inline-block;
  margin: 2rem auto 0 auto;
  padding: 0.7rem 2.1rem;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f34f29 0%, #ff7e29 100%);
  color: #fff;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #f34f2922;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.18s, box-shadow 0.18s, transform 0.13s;
  cursor: pointer;
  text-align: center;
}
.back-main-btn:hover {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff7e29 0%, #f34f29 100%);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px #f34f2944;
  transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.04);
  color: #fff;
}
@media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
  .git-header h1 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }
  .git-main-container {
    padding: 1.2rem 0.3rem 1.5rem 0.3rem;
  }
}
</style>
